    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical integrity is superlative; the Vanos system has been fully overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is current, offering a direct, tactile driving experience devoid of the typical wear found in lesser examples. This is a collector-grade specimen with flawless paint depth and a showroom-spec interior.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
