    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior retains that fresh, new-car scent, featuring supple leather and untouched trim. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships, with a complete folder of records to prove its pampered life. Garage-kept since day one and never driven in inclement weather, this car handles and performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands absolute perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
