    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is an absolute gem\u2014it genuinely looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it tucked away and spotless. If you're looking for something that's been truly babied and is in pristine shape, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! Let's get you behind the wheel of this beauty.",
