    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a benchmark-condition E46 M3, powered by the high-compression S54B32 power plant. This unit features individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated dual-VANOS system, delivering linear power across the entire rev range. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential with zero lash. Meticulously maintained, the vehicle includes proactive rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to address known chassis harmonics. With factory-spec alignment and impeccable bushings, the turn-in remains surgical. A true purist's specimen with zero mechanical compromises.",
